	<procedure>
		<step>
			<para>
				Make each user of your directory service that you want to have access to <productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> a member of one of these groups.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Configure</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configuration</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, then click on the <guilabel>Settings</guilabel> accordion, then <guilabel>Zones</guilabel>, then the <guilabel>Authentication</guilabel> tab, you can enable <guilabel>Get User Groups from LDAP</guilabel> after typing in all of the required settings. See <xref linkend="LDAP_Settings" />.
			</para>
		</step>
